description:
Just tested it. Running the program opens a top bar notification saying one shall press Alt+Space, and that sounds very promising (I'm looking for a Launchy alternative, having just switched from Windows, and Launchy won't be installed on Ubuntu 20.04 at all, unfortunately).

But then it just doesn't do anything when I press the said keys-combination. Dang.
Same issue as the previous two reviews. Something wrong when using Ubuntu 20.4.3
summary: This software has a problem, it does not do anything
